title: Who is the best wide receiver in the Lehigh Valley? (VOTE)
text:
By Greg Joyce | For lehighvalleylive.com on October 07, 2015 12:00 PM 
It's time to hear who you think is the top wide receiver in the Lehigh Valley. 
Last week, the fans voted Bethlehem Catholic's Antwon Keenan as the area's best running back. 
Now we've nominated 21 of the top wideouts through the first five weeks of the season and want to know your opinion on who is the best. 
Vote in the poll below , or write in the comments section if we're missing your pick. 
Please note, the results of this poll have no bearing on end-of-the-season All-Area honors.
